### Phase 1: Foundation & Backend Core

**Goal:** Build the "Skeleton" that holds the data.

* [x] **Project Init:** Install Laravel, Breeze (React/Inertia), and initialize Shadcn UI.
* [ ] **Database Migrations:**
* `courses`: title, slug, description, price, status (draft/published).
* `modules`: course_id, title, weight (for ordering).
* `lessons`: module_id, title, content, type (video/text/quiz), weight.
* `enrollments`: user_id, course_id, enrolled_at.


* [ ] **Models & Relations:** Set up HasMany/BelongsTo relationships for the above.
* [ ] **Admin Course CRUD:**
* Create `CourseController` for basic resource actions.
* Build a "Create Course" form using Shadcn `Form` and `Input` components.


* [ ] **The "Builder" UI:**
* A single-page interface to add modules and lessons via Inertia modals.
* *Bonus:* Add drag-and-drop ordering for lessons using `@dnd-kit/core`.


* [ ] **Landing Page:** A public route fetching all "Published" courses and displaying them in a Shadcn `Card` grid.

